<HEADLINE>
U.S. AND CANADIAN SALMON TREATY HAILED AS MAJOR STEP FORWARD 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By JOEL CONNELLY  
 c.1999 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
<TEXT>
