<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-04 01:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2668 &Cx1f; tth-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MOLEST-PASTOR-SPI &LR;      06-04 0962
