loudspeakers at this refugee camp broadcast the news of a potential
peace agreement for Kosovo, Ahmet Sharifi burst out laughing.
``Milosevic is lying again,'' he said. Such skepticism was echoed
on the sidelines of the men's round-robin volleyball game and in
the line of women filling their water jugs at an open spigot. By
