directed by Jon Turteltaub with Anthony Hopkins and Cuba Gooding,
Jr.
</P>
<P>
   LIMBO-FILM-REVIEW _ Stephen Holden reviews ``Limbo,'' by John
Sayles with David Straithairn, Mary Elizabeth Mastrantonio, Casey
Siemaszko.
</P>
<P>
   IRISH-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ Michiko Kakutani reviews ``Who's
Irish,'' by Gish Jen (Knopf).
</P>
