high school here, her mom lives in Dripping Springs and she got
married here, to another former Austinite. Ecklund used to be deaf
(she lost her hearing progressively after age 6) but recently her
hearing was restored, after she underwent a medical procedure
called a cochlear implant. Her character on Guiding Light is also
deaf; but now the character will have her hearing restored too.
Talking to Amy (and her audiologist in NYC) about the surgery and
how it has changed her life. With courtesy art from Guiding Light.
(Santos, Austin American-Statesman)
