<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-RUSSIA-PRIMAKOV-INTRIGUE-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DEMOCRACY 
</HEADLINE>
  
 IN RUSSIA, ENDLESS INTRIGUES and CLUELESS LEADERS, BUT LIMITED &HT;     (This has already moved to clients of Mikhail Gorbachev's
