</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-KOSOVO-CLINTON-0605-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    WITH KOSOVO PEACE PLAN, CLINTON APPEARS TO PULL VICTORY FROM
JAWS OF DEFEAT-- BUT WITH A PRICE
 &HT;    1000&AMP;ADD
 &HT;    With KOSOVO-KLA-0605.
 &HT;    EDs: An analysis sig may be used with this story.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By BOB DEANS 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service 
