   L I F E S T Y L E &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   CLIBURN-AMATEURS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   EDMOND, Okla. _ After overcoming drug addiction and putting a
prison term behind him, one of the contestants in the upcoming
