<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
June 5 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Eddie Ibardolasa at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
RAC-BELMONT (Elmont, N.Y.) _ The Daily Racing Form, in a rare
display of whimsy, printed photographs this week showing the facial
similarities between Charismatic and Secretariat. Chestnut coats,
white stars on foreheads, trickles of white on sharply tapered
noses. The resemblance is uncanny even by equine standards. Does it
end there? Has Charismatic inherited the Triple Crown gene from his
great-grandsire as well? 
By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
RAC-MODESTI-COLUMN (Elmont, N.Y.) _ Column from the Belmont
Stakes. 
By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBO-DODGERS-ANGELS (Los Angeles) _ The Los Angeles Dodgers face the
Anaheim Angels at 7:10 p.m. PDT. 
By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBC-NCAA-USC (Stanford, Calif.) _ USC baseball team (36-24) faces
Stanford (46-13) in the NCAA Super Regional at 7 p.m. PDT. 
By Chris Branam. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBN-DODGERNOTES (Los Angeles) _ Dodgers notebook. 
By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-ANGELS (Los Angeles) _ Angels sidebar from game at Dodger
Stadium. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-ANGELNOTES (Los Angeles) _ Angels notebook. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 

