   RAC-BELMONT (Belmont, N.Y.) _ As many as 80,000 could be on hand
Saturday afternoon to see if Charismatic can jump from the ranks of
racing's blue collar workers and into immortality. By Michael
Madden.
</P>
<P>
   MCDONOUGH-COLUMN (Undated) _ Developments in the lawuit against
doctors who treated the late Celtics star Reggie Lewis. By Will
McDonough.
</P>
<P>
   TEN-COLLINS-COLUMN (Paris) _ With flair, Andrei Medvedev makes
it to the finals at the French Open. By Bud Collins.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
