<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-04 20:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3710 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOMELESS-SUIT-HNS &LR;      06-04 0999
