Vladimir Shabalin with samples of his vodka collection at his vodka
library in the town some 200 miles north of Moscow. Shabalin and
his partners are part of a scattered effort to create a new,
upscale culture of drinking the ancient spirit. (Jacqueline Mia
Foster/New York Times Photo) LITE
</P>
